7. Functions and Procedures

7.1 Function Declaration

```pascal
function add(a: int32, b: int32): int32
begin
    return a + b
end
```

7.2 Procedure Declaration

```pascal
procedure greet(name: string)
begin
    writeln("Hello, ", name)
end
```

7.3 Generic Functions

```pascal
function identity<T>(value: T): T
begin
    return value
end
```

7.4 Comptime Functions

```pascal
@comptime
function factorial(n: int32): int32
begin
    var result: int32 := 1
    for i in 2..n do
        result *= i
    end
    return result
end

const FACT_10 := factorial(10)  // Computed at compile time
```

7.5 Async Functions (Maia)

```pascal
async function fetch_data(url: string): string
begin
    var response := await http.get(url)
    return response.body
end
```

