10. Concurrency

10.1 Actors

```pascal
actor Counter {
    var _count: iso int32 := 0
    
    behavior increment()
    begin
        _count += 1
    end
    
    function get(): val int32
    begin
        return _count as val
    end
}
```

10.2 Channels

```pascal
var ch: channel(int32) := channel.create(10)
ch.send(42)
var value := ch.recv()
```

10.3 Spawning

```pascal
var handle := spawn worker()
wait(handle)
```

10.4 Async/Await (Maia)

```pascal
async function fetch(): string
begin
    return await http.get(url)
end

var data := await fetch()
```

