11. Safety Features

11.1 Safety Levels

Level Bounds Overflow Use-After-Free Leak Detection
full ✅ ✅ ✅ ✅
release ✅ ✅ ❌ ❌
os ✅ ❌ ❌ ❌
none ❌ ❌ ❌ ❌

11.2 Safe/Unsafe Blocks

```pascal
safe do
    arr[i] := 42  // Bounds checked
end

unsafe do
    arr[i] := 42  // No checks
    asm { mov eax, 42 }
end
```

11.3 Option Type (Null Safety)

```pascal
var maybe: ?int32 := null

if maybe |value| then
    writeln(value)
end
```

